**Segments**

The DevOps market is segmented based on components, deployment mode, organization size, industry vertical, and geography. By components, the market is categorized into solutions and services. Solutions segment includes monitoring and performance management, lifecycle management, analytics, delivery and operations, and testing and development. Services segment comprises consulting, integration, and training and support. In terms of deployment mode, the market is divided into cloud and on-premises. Organization size segmentation includes small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and large enterprises. Industry vertical segmentation covers IT and telecom, BFSI, retail, healthcare, manufacturing, and others. Geographically, the market is segmented into North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, South America, and Middle East & Africa.

